ion website https://ask.loc.gov/map-geography/. Title supplied by cataloger. Maps in this collection dated before 1887 are photocopies or facsimiles. Maps in this collection that may be in copyright are not available online. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. HI-19-01 through HI-19-27."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:51.023Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-07", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-07"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021589615/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:19:hi-019:hi-019-01-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:19:hi-019:hi-019-01-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=741&w=588", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:19:hi-019:hi-019-01-01/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=1483&w=1176"], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["honolulu", "united states", "hawaii"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["sheet", "2024-01-31t13:30:40", "2021589615", "2025-06-07t10:47:29.700000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map", "collection"], "other_title": ["Alternate supplied title: Hawaii title collection--drawer 19", "Alternate supplied title: Hawaii title collection--cities and towns Honolulu 1816-1927"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "catalog", "cities and towns", "single sheet maps, title collection", "geography and map division"], "score": 28.993853, "shelf_id": "G4384.H6 coll .M3 drawer 19", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["real property", "landowners", "tourist maps", "hawaii", "honolulu (hawaii)", "honolulu", "united states", "maps"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:21:53.023Z", "title": "[Maps of Hawaii--cities and towns Honolulu 1816 to 1927]", "type": ["cartographic"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021589615/"}, {"access