17"], "description": ["Ml HAWAIIAN GAZETTE Entered at the Postoffice of Honolulu H T Secondclass Matter SemiWeekly Issued Tuesdays and Fridays WALTER G SMITH Editor Subscription Rates Per Month 25 1 Per Month Foreign J300lPer Tear Foreign TUESDAY S 35 400 Payable Invariably in Advance CHARLES S CRANE Manager DECEMBER 17 TRANSPORTATION PROBLEM IN AUSTRALIA Hawaii is not the only country that is wrestling with the transportation problem or that has wrestled with it recently In the commonwealth of Australia steamship communication with Great Britain has been a political issue for several years and has at least once had its influence in putting one ministry out and another one in It was evidently a matter of very great satisfaction to the present ministry of that commonwealth when it was able to announce last month the completed negotiation of a contract with the Orient Steam Navigation Company for a fortnightly service between common wealth ports and the United Kingdom under conditions as to speed and freights and accommodations which it believed would prove satisfactory to the public As this contract will have some effect at least on the activity of the com monwealth in securing a line of mail steamers between Australian ports and"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T07:58:52.187Z", "group": ["ndnp/hihouml", "university-of-hawaii-at-manoa-honolulu-hi-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83025121/1907-12-17/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:hihouml:batch_hihouml_cardinal_ver01:data:sn83025121:00294552303:1907121701:0175/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=453&w=316", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:hihouml:batch_hihouml_cardinal_ver01:data:sn83025121:00294552303:1907121701:0175/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=907&w=633", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/hihouml/batch_hihouml_cardinal_ver01/data/sn83025121/00